gnm:Cells.gnm:Cell: This table is the solution to the problem of finding a plane for a set of points (X, Y, H)
DATA sheet - contains the coordinates of the original points and the transition to the plane.
OLS sheet - contains the solution of normal equations and finding the parameters of the plane.
REVERSE sheet - contains the reverse transition from the plane to the original coordinates.
HOW TO: Not all input data can give a stable solution.
